* Garden of Souls (WIP Name) is an Action Adventure game with RPG and puzzle elements!


* It is heavily inspired by the Zelda series, but aims to have a bigger, more explorable world, make more complex puzzles and have deeper, skill based and faster paced combat.

Story
---------

* The story follows Vanylla, a young gorl with telekinetic powers who has been living peacefully in an isolated utopian landscape with her father and brother. Her peaceful lifestyle abruptly comes to an end when her brother is kidnapped by a powerful stranger, with her barely leaving unscatched after her father came to the rescue. Vanylla then sets on a journey to rescue her brother, and learn the truth about herself and the seemingly utopian land she lives in.

Play the demo for the prologue!

Gameplay
